column6: Thunderbolts vs. Agents of Atlas-round 2! The hunt down in the swamp comes to a head when one of the T-Bolts ends up dead! There's not going to be much time to cope either, because Norman Osborn needs his team of killers ready for a final mission-and this is what he's been saving them for! Rated T  ...$2.99
